{
  "stem": "19198.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 238.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The director of the school, who was a registered Democrat, walked out and said, I refuse to teach under this flag.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was immediately arrested.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was very lucky in that they just reduced his rank from director to teacher.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we realized that [LAUGHS] a different wind was blowing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The attitude of-- of teachers did change, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those who, prior to the arrival of the Nazi government, may have been quiet members of the Nazi party, they became the big shots.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first thing that I-- that I learned at the end of the school year-- which in Germany, or at least in our state, was around April-- the-- the custom in-- in the school was that the first student, the top student in each class, got a prize.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every student got-- every first student got a prize, except I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I kept my first position, because that was the statistics, but the-- the teacher in charge of the class was a Nazi, and he said, in my class, no Jew will get a prize, period.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but it was not in any violent or crass way, but a slow process of not just not being part of the-- of the group, of not being invited to parties, and all that type of thing.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the-- as long as I was in high school, both in Eberbach and later in Heidelberg, scholastically, there was no major change.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not really, although I was conscious that under certain circumstances, there might be.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- as far as I recall, I-- I never was especially self-conscious on the-- on the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
